⚙️ Dockerfile Breakdown
Base Image: Used a lightweight Alpine Linux image with OpenJDK 17
FROM openjdk:17-jdk-alpine

Set Working Directory:
WORKDIR /app

Copy Java File into Container:
COPY src/Main.java /app/Main.java

Compile the Java Program:
RUN javac Main.java

Run the Program:
CMD ["java", "Main"]

